OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FAny
OL,6,Fremaining showers will fade away,
OL,7,Fleaving a largely dry evening with
OL,8,Flight winds. Cloud will increase from
OL,9,Fthe west later, bringing outbreaks of
OL,10,Frain before dawn. Winds freshening
OL,11,Flater.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSaturday:FMostly cloudy with outbreaks
OL,14,Fof rain gradually transferring north-
OL,15,Feastwards through the morning. Some
OL,16,Fbrighter intervals develop for a time,
OL,17,Fbut further heavy afternoon showers
OL,18,Ffollowing, perhaps thundery. Breezy at
OL,19,Ftimes.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
