OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:
OL,6,FIncreasingly cloudy and breezy on
OL,7,FSunday, with patchy light rain late.
OL,8,FEarly rain clearing east Monday, sunny
OL,9,Fspells, scattered showers following.
OL,10,FCooler and showery Tuesday. Showers
OL,11,Foccasionally heavy, perhaps thundery.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
